http://ftp.x.org/pub/individual/proto/xf86bigfontproto-1.2.0.tar.bz2
http://ftp.x.org/pub/individual/proto/xf86driproto-2.1.1.tar.bz2
http://ftp.x.org/pub/individual/proto/xf86dgaproto-2.1.tar.bz2
